'''天鹅演习'''（{{lang-en|Exercise Cygnus}}）是{{link-en|英国国家医疗服务体系|NHS England}}在2016年10月进行的一次模拟演习，旨在评估假设的[[亚洲流感|亚洲流感]]（H2N2）疫情对[[英国|英国]]的影响。<ref>{{Cite web|title=POWYS PANDEMIC INFLUENZA PLANNING UPDATE 2016|url=http://www.powysthb.wales.nhs.uk/sitesplus/documents/1145/Board%5FItem%5F2.6%5F%20Pandemic%20flu%20Annual%20Report.pdf|date=2017-01-25|last=Bale|first=Donna|work=powysthb.wales.nhs.uk|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200503223929/http://www.powysthb.wales.nhs.uk/sitesplus/documents/1145/Board%5FItem%5F2.6%5F%20Pandemic%20flu%20Annual%20Report.pdf|archivedate=2020-05-03|dead-url=no|access-date=2020-08-25}}</ref><ref name="Telegraph-2020-03-28">{{Cite news|last=Nuki|first=Paul|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/03/28/exercise-cygnus-uncovered-pandemic-warnings-buried-government/|title=Exercise Cygnus uncovered: the pandemic warnings buried by the government|date=2020-03-28|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2020-08-25|last2=Gardner|first2=Bill|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235|archivedate=2020-08-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828232841/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/03/28/exercise-cygnus-uncovered-pandemic-warnings-buried-government/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pegg">{{cite web|title=What was Exercise Cygnus and what did it find?|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/may/07/what-was-exercise-cygnus-and-what-did-it-find|accessdate=2020-08-25|author=David Pegg|date=2020-05-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904120008/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/may/07/what-was-exercise-cygnus-and-what-did-it-find|archivedate=2020-09-04|dead-url=no|newspaper=The Guardian}}</ref>演习结果显示，此次疫情将导致英国卫生系统因资源匮乏而崩溃。<ref name="Telegraph-2020-03-28" /><ref name="Guardian">{{Cite news|last=Carrington|first=Damian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/mar/29/uk-strategy-to-address-pandemic-threat-not-properly-implemented|title=UK strategy to address pandemic threat 'not properly implemented'|date=2020-03-29|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2020-08-25|dead-url=no|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archivedate=2020-08-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826140148/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2020/mar/29/uk-strategy-to-address-pandemic-threat-not-properly-implemented}}</ref>当时的首席医疗官{{link-en|萨利·戴维斯|Sally Davies (doctor)}}表示，缺乏[[呼吸机|医用呼吸机]]和尸体处理的后勤保障的问题是十分严重。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Government documents show no planning for ventilators in the event of a pandemic|url=https://www.newstatesman.com/politics/health/2020/03/government-documents-show-no-planning-ventilators-event-pandemic|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-03-16|last=Lambert|first=Harry|work=New Statesman|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826140042/https://www.newstatesman.com/politics/health/2020/03/government-documents-show-no-planning-ventilators-event-pandemic|archivedate=2020-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Smyth|first=Chris|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/nhs-fails-to-cope-with-bodies-in-flu-pandemic-test-8pnmdpdfx|title=NHS fails to cope with bodies in flu pandemic test|date=27 December 2016|work=The Times|accessdate=2020-08-25|dead-url=no|language=en|issn=0140-0460|archivedate=2020-08-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829005134/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/nhs-fails-to-cope-with-bodies-in-flu-pandemic-test-8pnmdpdfx}}</ref>截至2020年4月，演习的全部结果仍是机密。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nick Ferrari's extraordinary exchange with Care Minister over pandemic test exercise|url=https://www.lbc.co.uk/radio/presenters/nick-ferrari/extraordinary-exchange-care-minister-coronavirus/|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-03-30|last=|first=|work=LBC|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200621091930/https://www.lbc.co.uk/radio/presenters/nick-ferrari/extraordinary-exchange-care-minister-coronavirus/|archivedate=2020-06-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》报道，一位政府消息人士称，模拟结果 “太可怕了”（{{lang|en|too terrifying}}），不能透露。<ref name="Telegraph-2020-03-28" />据《每日电讯报》报道，这次演习导致一种设想产生，即“[[群体免疫|群体免疫]]”的方法将是对类似[[流行病|流行病]]的最佳对策。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Hope|first=Christopher|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2020/04/24/jeremy-hunt-says-has-no-problem-governments-2016-pandemic-report/|title=Jeremy Hunt says he has no problem with Government's 2016 pandemic report being published|date=2020-04-24|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2020-08-25|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235|archivedate=2020-09-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916170724/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/politics/2020/04/24/jeremy-hunt-says-has-no-problem-governments-2016-pandemic-report/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一些新闻报道根据“天鹅演习”得出的结论，批评英国政府对[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]的处理。<ref name="Telegraph-2020-03-28" /><ref name="Guardian" />

2020年4月底，《[[观察家报|观察家报]]》报道称，政府因要求公布研究结果而受到法律诉讼的威胁<ref>{{Cite news|last=Doward|first=Jamie|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2020/apr/26/doctor-sue-results-operation-cygnus|title=If ministers fail to reveal 2016 flu study they ‘will face court’|date=2020-04-26|work=The Observer|accessdate=2020-08-25|language=en-GB|issn=0029-7712|archivedate=2020-08-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829001337/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2020/apr/26/doctor-sue-results-operation-cygnus|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这份被列为“官方-敏感”（Official - Sensitive）的报告于2020年5月7日被泄露，并全文发表在《[[卫报|卫报]]》上（除被隐去的部分联系方式）。<ref name="pegg" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Revealed: the secret report that gave ministers warning of care home coronavirus crisis|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/may/07/revealed-the-secret-report-that-gave-ministers-warning-of-care-home-coronavirus-crisis|accessdate=2020-08-25|date=2020-05-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200828083738/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/may/07/revealed-the-secret-report-that-gave-ministers-warning-of-care-home-coronavirus-crisis|archivedate=2020-08-28|dead-url=no|first1=David|last1=Pegg|first2=Robert|last2=Booth|first3=David|last3=Conn|via=theguardian.com}}</ref>

